plugins.name: Asana
plugins.description:
Improve your productivity by creating tasks in Asana directly
from Sentry issues. This integration also allows you to link Sentry
issues to existing tasks in Asana.

featureDescriptions.description:
Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to an Asana ticket in any of your
            projects, providing a quick way to jump from a Sentry bug to tracked ticket!
Link Sentry issues to existing Asana tickets.

plugins.name: Bitbucket
plugins.description: Integrate Bitbucket issues by linking a repository to a project.

featureDescriptions.description:
Track commits and releases (learn more
            [here](https://docs.sentry.io/learn/releases/))
Create Bitbucket issues from Sentry
Link Sentry issues to existing Bitbucket issues

plugins.name: GitHub
plugins.description: Integrate GitHub issues by linking a repository to a project.

featureDescriptions.description:
Authorize repositories to be added to your Sentry organization to augment
            sentry issues with commit data with [deployment
            tracking](https://docs.sentry.io/learn/releases/).

Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to a GitHub issue or pull
            request in any of your repositories, providing a quick way to jump from
            Sentry bug to tracked issue or PR!

plugins.name: GitLab
plugins.description: Integrate GitLab issues by linking a repository to a project

featureDescriptions.description:
Track commits and releases (learn more
            [here](https://docs.sentry.io/learn/releases/))

Resolve Sentry issues via GitLab commits and merge requests by
            including `Fixes PROJ-ID` in the message
Create GitLab issues from Sentry
Link Sentry issues to existing GitLab issues

plugins.name: Heroku
plugins.doc:
Add a Sentry release webhook to automatically track new releases.

heroku webhooks:add -i api:release -l notify -u https://sentry.io/api/hooks/release/heroku/5942472/cd92fd5564e9d4a2b82dd03ad2d539a1a2b83ea13e2e205507d2f8d3c513d864/ -a YOUR_APP_NAME

featureDescriptions.description: Integrate Heroku release tracking.

plugins.name: JIRA
plugins.description: Integrate JIRA issues by linking a project.

featureDescriptions.description:
Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to a Jira ticket in any of your
            projects, providing a quick way to jump from a Sentry bug to tracked ticket!

plugins.name: OpsGenie
plugins.description:
Trigger alerts in Opsgenie from Sentry.

Opsgenie is a cloud-based service for dev & ops teams, providing reliable
alerts, on-call schedule management and escalations. OpsGenie integrates with
monitoring tools & services, ensures the right people are notified. This
plugin only supports issue alerts.

featureDescriptions.description: Manage incidents and outages by sending Sentry notifications to OpsGenie.
Configure Sentry rules to trigger notifications based on conditions you set.
Manage incidents and outages by sending Sentry notifications to PagerDuty.

Configure rule based PagerDuty alerts to automatically be triggered in a specific
            service - or in multiple services!

plugins.name: Phabricator
plugins.description:
Improve your productivity by creating tickets in Phabricator directly from Sentry issues.
This integration also allows you to link Sentry issues to existing tickets in Phabricator.

Phabricator is a set of tools for developing software. It includes applications for
code review, repository hosting, bug tracking, project management, and more.

featureDescriptions.description:
Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to a Phabricator ticket in any of your
            projects, providing a quick way to jump from a Sentry bug to tracked ticket!
Link Sentry issues to existing Phabricator tickets.

plugins.name: Pivotal Tracker
plugins.description:
Improve your productivity by creating tickets in Pivotal Tracker directly from Sentry issues.
This integration also allows you to link Sentry issues to existing tickets in Pivotal Tracker.

Pivotal Tracker is a straightforward project-planning tool that helps software development
teams form realistic expectations about when work might be completed based on the teams
ongoing performance. Tracker visualizes your projects in the form of stories
moving through your workflow, encouraging you to break down projects into manageable
chunks and have important conversations about deliverables and scope.

featureDescriptions.description:
Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to a Pivotal Tracker ticket in any of your
            projects, providing a quick way to jump from a Sentry bug to tracked ticket!
Link Sentry issues to existing Pivotal Tracker tickets.

plugins.name: Pushover
plugins.description:
Get notified of Sentry alerts on any device using the Pushover integration.

Pushover makes it easy to get real-time notifications on your Android, iPhone, iPad, and Desktop.

featureDescriptions.description: Have Pushover notifications get sent to your mobile device with the Pushover app.
Configure Sentry rules to trigger notifications based on conditions you set.

plugins.name: Redmine
plugins.description:
Create issues in Redmine directly from Sentry. This integration also
allows you to link Sentry issues to existing tickets in Redmine.

Redmine is a flexible project management web application. Written using
the Ruby on Rails framework, it is cross-platform and cross-database.

featureDescriptions.description:
Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to an Redmine issue in any of your
            projects, providing a quick way to jump from a Sentry bug to tracked ticket!
Link Sentry issues to existing Redmine issue.
Watch the SessionStack session replay of a user in a video widget embedded in the Sentry UI for an issue.

plugins.name: Slack
plugins.description: Post notifications to a Slack channel.

featureDescriptions.description:
Configure rule based Slack notifications to automatically be posted into a
            specific channel. Want any error that's happening more than 100 times a
            minute to be posted in `#critical-errors`? Setup a rule for it!

plugins.name: Trello
plugins.description:
Create cards in Trello directly from Sentry. This integration also allows
you to link Sentry issues to existing cards in Trello.

Trello is the easy, free, flexible, and visual way to manage your projects
and organize anything, trusted by millions of people from all over the world.

featureDescriptions.description:
Create and link Sentry issue groups directly to an Trello card in any of your
            projects, providing a quick way to jump from a Sentry bug to tracked ticket!
Link Sentry issues to existing Trello cards

plugins.name: Twilio (SMS)
plugins.description:
Get notified of Sentry alerts via SMS.

Twilio allows users to send and receive text messages globally with
the API that over a million developers depend on.

featureDescriptions.description: Set up SMS notifications to be sent to your mobile device via Twilio.
Configure Sentry rules to trigger notifications based on conditions you set.

plugins.name: VictorOps
plugins.description:
Trigger alerts in VictorOps from Sentry.

VictorOps is incident response software purpose-built for teams powering the
evolution of software. With on-call basics, cross-team collaboration, and
streamlined visibility, we champion the engineers powering innovation and uptime.

featureDescriptions.description: Manage incidents and outages by sending Sentry notifications to VictorOps.
Configure Sentry rules to trigger notifications based on conditions you set.

plugins.name: WebHooks
plugins.description:
Trigger outgoing HTTP POST requests from Sentry.

Note: To configure webhooks over multiple projects, we recommend setting up an
Internal Integration.

featureDescriptions.description: Configure rule based outgoing HTTP POST requests from Sentry.
